  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK583">
<l>oṟṟiṉā ṉoṟṟip poruṭeriyā maṉṉavaṉ </l>
<l> koṟṟaṅ koḷakkiṭanta til</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There is no way for a king to obtain conquests, who knows not the advantage of discoveries made by a spy.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
